Birthday date as an ISO 8601 datetime string.
.TP
.B calendar
Object with
.BR id ,
.BR title ,
.BR type ,
.BR source ,
and
.B color
fields.
.PP
.B Week
.PP
A JSON object with week information:
.TP
.B week
Week number (1\-53).
.TP
.B year
The year the week belongs to (may differ from the calendar year for
