.RS
.nf
$ ical\-guy reminders list \-\-completed \-\-include\-lists Work
.fi
.RE
.PP
List available reminder lists:
.PP
.RS
.nf
$ ical\-guy reminders lists
.fi
.RE
.PP
Show current week number:
.PP
.RS
.nf
$ ical\-guy week
.fi
.RE
.PP
Show next week's number:
.PP
.RS
.nf
$ ical\-guy week \-\-next 1
.fi
.RE
.PP
Show the Sunday of the current week:
.PP
.RS
.nf
$ ical\-guy week \-\-start\-date
.fi
.RE
.PP
Check for conflicts today:
.PP
.RS
.nf
$ ical\-guy conflicts
.fi
.RE
.PP
Check for conflicts this week:
.PP
.RS
.nf
$ ical\-guy conflicts \-\-from today \-\-to today+7
.fi
.RE
.PP
Find free time today:
.PP
.RS
.nf
$ ical\-guy free
.fi
.RE
